Invocation Name: lehigh vegan
des: List of vegetarian and vegan restaurant options in and around the Lehigh Valley. Easton, Allentown, Bethlehem, and Stroudsburg Pennsylvania. Includes addresses, phone number, and brief descriptions which can be heard from Alexa, and read in the companion Alexa app. To enable, say "Alexa, enable Lehigh Vegan." Then to use, simply say, "Alexa, ask Lehigh Vegan for a fact."
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
